# Test fixture fonts

Both fonts are bundled solely for use in the test suite. They are not
redistributed as part of the public opal package; they live in the
`tests/fixtures/fonts/` directory and are not exported to consumers of
the library.

## Inter-Regular.ttf

- Copyright 2016 The Inter Project Authors
- SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1
- Source: https://github.com/rsms/inter (release 4.0)

## IBMPlexSerif-Regular.ttf

- Copyright 2020 IBM Corp. All rights reserved.
- SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1
- Source: https://github.com/IBM/plex (release @ibm/plex-serif@2.0.0)
